Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:40.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to go out and buzz around again, Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:41.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:47.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have a training assignment from Dux Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:51.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aren’t you guys busy with your own duties?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, and we’re exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:58.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,On night patrols, we have to be more careful than in daytime, and we run into the enemy more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fluttering around in daytime is child’s play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you guys… before…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:09.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,You only flew daytime patrols, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Weren’t {\i1}we{\i0} always the ones who took the night shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, things are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:20.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re the top choir on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} now. Us. Chor Rubor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you don’t like it, you’re welcome to try to prove yourselves again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:27.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way. We’re tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let them by, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:38.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the way, which Ri Maajon are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Dandelion Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Dandelion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:46.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a ceremonial Ri Maajon used to show diplomatic courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s the use of practicing an old-fashioned thing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I left some snacks on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:58.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat them, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t wake me up when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:07.20,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Over International Waters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, they’ve fixed her up beautifully!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:37.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,These kids really worked hard at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s a real antique, but it looks like they did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Grandpa flew her when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather was a Simoun sibylla, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:50.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,After he went to the Spring, this old Simile was his prized possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:25.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,When {\i1}we{\i0} used to have night duty, those guys were always jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Rubor…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They{\i0} used to make way for {\i1}us{\i0} whenever they saw Neviril coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take pride in who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:39.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,As a member of Chor Tempest,\NI want to make this choir the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:45.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to make Tempest the best choir, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:51.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because you won’t have to go to the Spring as long as we’re a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to go right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then just go, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to go there with the one who’s most important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:07.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,And then, when we came out of the Spring, I’d be a man, and she would be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the two of you could just do it right there on the floor, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:21.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we want to be the best choir, we’ll need two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:26.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unless we get two more members, we won’t be able to fly six Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,With Neviril and Aaeru as a pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,we’d have a good shot at being the best choir again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, are you giving up on Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:51.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s do it in front of Arcus Prima, where Neviril and the dux can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, we’re supposed to be higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I’m just not good enough for the Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please concentrate, Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You lead everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, who’s the one you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, Floe, you’ve really been developing a bad rep lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not true, Alti!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you really need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:35.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you feel the same way about me, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:41.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn’t like me, after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:42.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Concentrate on your flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:58.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we can’t be at the rendezvous yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s definitely the {\i1}Niger{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe there’s an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:08.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe there are some VIPs who are in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:11.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’d better get the kids from Tempest back on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niger{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s supposed to be stationed west of the Grand Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a Simile Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s up with these guys? They suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can’t even catch the speaker cable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re doing it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:07.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}this{\i0} Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:09:01.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Plumbum Highlanders have similar customs to our Holy Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I doubt that there is anything in our decorations to offend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:08.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,This Tempus Spatium image should be covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,But won’t that make us look weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:15.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Highlanders worship a god called Animus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:20.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Historically, Animus and Tempus Spatium
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,may well have been the same deity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:26.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,but neither the Theocracy nor the Highland government recognizes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose we should remove any unnecessary irritants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:35.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,For the sake of peace, Tempus Spatium will be happy to be covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:07.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,A peace… conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:14.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now, our country is at war with all of the other countries around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of them are in a bad shape economically, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,They want our Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’ll do anything to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:25.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,More precisely, it’s the helical motors inside that they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:29.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ve only been able to dig them up from the ancient ruins, and they’re what let the Simoun fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:35.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the peace proposal came from the Plumbum Highlands, to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:40.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,The first peace talks will be held over the ocean, in international waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Naturally, it will be kept secret from the other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:46.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the conference will be held on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t matter what the politicians do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ll still be free to do Maaju in the pool… I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:54.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,But they might confine us to our quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! It’s them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:59.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are the guys who were in that Simile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are they doing wandering around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are they on our ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances, I’d say they were replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, I bet she’ll say something like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,“Chor Tempest, you don’t live up to your reputation.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Members of Chor Tempest, I apologize for my earlier behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It really was you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:42.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I can see that you don’t live up to your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:58.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something funny… Lady Rodoreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course you wouldn’t remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:11.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was just one girl among dozens of servants in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:44.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, you remember me. I’m honoured…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have been transferred from Chor Ignis on the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,as replacements for Chor Tempest’s losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Mamiina, reporting as ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please treat me as one of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve been transferred to Chor Tempest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve got just one thing to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hate war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:15.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Help! Please, somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Sibylla Aurea’s room…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s happened to Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:36.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:40.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:49.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Sibylla Aurea is allowed a private stateroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is recognized as her privilege.
Comment: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,From now on, she’ll have a roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para, it’s been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:03.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. My apologies for not calling on you, Mr. Vice Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:09.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think this is a good way for you and your new pair to become close as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:11.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,New pair…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, then that’s my bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,“New pair!”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. I’m giving you Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pairs form naturally, and only when both partners agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were a sibylla too, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You must know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:47.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Neviril, those days are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,You need a new pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you carry on like this, your reputation will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Although I have been always an auriga,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:59.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,if I could be your pair, I would have no objection to being the sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina does not come from sibylla family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:10.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,But of all the sibyllae at the Grand Temple, she had the best record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:12.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Maajon of the Raging Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Tsunami Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can do them more perfectly than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those Ri Maajons are the dangerous ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:22.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can kill the largest number of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:26.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s time for you to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand that you’ve been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:35.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I know you can get past that and shine again as the Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:39.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if I do, your position will be secure, won’t it, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:44.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don’t understand your feelings, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you hate fighting, you can go to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You would make a most beautiful daughter, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:57.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if you don’t want to go to the Spring, and you won’t fly Simoun, then what…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:16:00.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,“…answer can you give me?” Is that what you were going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s long past time for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does this mean that Neviril’s coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aaeru, now you can be my pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:14.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ve still got my eye on Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:18.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neviril’s just {\i1}sooo{\i0} popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:21.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess I’ll have to give up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:25.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll go with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,But no matter who it is, I’m not gonna like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you hate it so much, why don’t you go to the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:43.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most of the other priestesses I knew were sent off to fight and die because they could fly Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:47.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t be the only one to skip out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that’s why you’re here, it sounds like you have a death wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:06.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had always hoped that you and Neviril would become a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mr. Vice Chairman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:11.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will {\i1}always{\i0} protect Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:56.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Mamiina. I’m still…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,be my pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Mamiina,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,even if you take my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,you will never be my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, understand this:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,one way or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} be your pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,My goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you climb down from your window on that rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a funny girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:09.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Dandelion Ri Maajon requires all six Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Currently, Chor Tempest…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,…is at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shouldn’t that be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:19.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,But can they do it so soon after absorbing new members?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The peace conference with the Highlanders is and important occasion for prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:26.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can’t afford to take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:31.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I require Chor Tempest to perform this Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they are incapable of doing that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,What would you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:41.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do not intend to let my daughter be sullied any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will not let her be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you here to challenge me to a Maaju contest, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,A contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,For who gets to be Neviril’s pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is no contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:22.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,In the pool, if you’re wearing one of these suits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,the helical motors will interact with the suit and let you fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,But take away the suit…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:28.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Say you’ll give up Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop being stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:34.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m {\i1}going{\i0} to be Neviril’s pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s what I want, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:37.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that’s Neviril’s decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t even come from a good family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:41.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re only here because you’re good at flying Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:44.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You aren’t worthy of Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you’re just the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:20:59.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:09.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can Chor Tempest be of any use if this is how you behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:13.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… that was…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,When the peace conference is over, Chor Tempest…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,…will be disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:23.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, please, Mr. Vice Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that happens, your own daughter…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s even more reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:30.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,No daughter of mine is going to stay in a choir like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sending her to the Spring before she gets hurt any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:37.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um… but what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:39.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m disappointed in you.
